responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "CD3468EA43C3178030FFB1995D817124", "So you\'re one of the mercs, but you sure don\'t look the part. I have a list from the higher ups and, well, it says you\'re hunting a farmhand, lucky you. He\'s a serf who owes some dues is my guess, but a high price to pay if you ask me. Description here says he\'s a dodgy fella, but he won\'t be expecting this kind of trouble, so you\'ll find him at Paragon Ranch unarmed no doubt.")
